              },
              {
                "type": "rich_text_section",
                "elements": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The GBG offers a serious play structure for truth seekers to sincerely explore topics together."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "rich_text_section",
                "elements": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Players choose a topic – a bead – and take time-limited turns – 2 minutes, 1 minute, 30 seconds – to improvise an unfiltered flow of cocreation."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "rich_text_section",
                "elements": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " A great turn expresses the most truth in the smallest space, and intertwines closely with the previous turn. But a great player knows when to redirect the flow, when to reflect back, when to ask questions, and when to increase or decrease the level of abstraction."
